result.name: Rakuraku Ramen

reviews.text: This may perhaps be the worst experience I’ve ever had in any Japanese restaurant. We ordered a salad, edamame (枝豆) and ramen. The salad is flooded with sesame sauce, it was really unacceptable as I felt like I’m drinking the sauce rather than eating the veggies. It’s very unhealthy as well. The edamame is a huge disappointment as well. It’s covered with salt so it’s too salty. We have to remove some of the salt by drinking water. The ramen is too oily.

Pretty delicious food for the price
Affordable ramen and the other side dishes tasted good too
not worth that price
